[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man dies in early morning Abergavenny roundabout crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 61-year-old man has died following an early morning road crash in Monmouthshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Gwent Police said it received reports of a one vehicle collision on the mini roundabout in Llanfoist, Abergavenny shortly before 5:30 BST.
The driver, who was local to the area, was taken to hospital but died from his injuries.
